Leonard Bernstein , the beloved internationally acclaimed maestro died on October 14th at 72 of lung failure .
Within days , the New York Philharmonic , in tribute to its 47-year association with the brilliant conductor played a special program , as did several other orchestras .
Recently , Broadway also honored Bernstein , composer of '' West Side Story , '' with a special show at the Majestic Theater .
Several record companies will accelerate re-releases of Bernstein recordings .
Bernstein though ill for some time , did participate in his 70th birthday celebrations at Tanglewood and Carnegie Hall .
The latter occurred on the 45th anniversary of his directorial debut with the Philharmonic .
